1.外容器relateCommendVideo，设置overflow-x: scroll;-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
2.内容器relateCommendVideoInner默认设置大宽度
3.子级设置不折行

.relateCommendVideo{
    padding:10px;
    overflow-y: hidden;
    overflow-x: scroll;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    background: #fff;
    margin-top:10px;
}
.relateCommendVideoInner{
    width:2000px;
}
.relateCommendVideoInner li{
    float:left;
    word-wrap: break-word;
    -ms-word-wrap: break-word;
    margin-right: 15px;
}
